        "This add-on is the CollectD and AuditD path, not the same package as Splunk_TA_nix.",
        "For metrics, use HEC with linux:collectd:http:metrics and create a metrics index before routing data to it.",
        "For HEC JSON events, set the HEC source type to linux:collectd:http:json.",
        "For Graphite over TCP, set the TCP source type to linux:collectd:graphite; TCP cannot collect metrics.",
        "For AuditD file or TCP collection, use source type linux:audit and set auditd log_format=ENRICHED for CIM mapping.",
        "Do not use Deployment Server to deploy configured credential-bearing copies of this add-on to many forwarders; the official docs flag credential-vault and duplicate collection risks.",
